name: DVD : The Art of Tonal Drawing
description: WAS: $99.00 In this DVD the Brazilian tattoo and fine artist Camila Rocha teaches the art of Tonal Drawing. This technique focuses on creating an illusion of reality by making a two dimensional image on paper that has the depth and look of a three dimensional figure. The tutorial will cover the organizational process, the use of values, how to understand forms, shapes and the behavior of light as it falls on the subject to create a realistic impression. The technique is introduced through a demo by Camila Rocha in which she creates a drawing based on a picture reference from the VIVA VAMPIRA! Exhibit at Kat Von D's Wonderland Gallery. • Feature Run Time Approx. 45 Minutes • 2012 • Color • Widescreen Presentation  • Full HD NTSC 1920x1080 •  Stereo 48Khz Audio Click HERE to watch a teaser of the DVD Camila Rocha
